{"id":101,"date":"2021-03-23T12:03:37","date_gmt":"2021-03-23T12:03:37","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wordpress\/wordpress\/?page_id=101"},"modified":"2021-03-31T06:46:35","modified_gmt":"2021-03-31T06:46:35","slug":"core-values","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/library.ttu.edu.gh\/index.php\/core-values\/","title":{"rendered":"Core Values"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><style>\n    p,figure{\n      \n      color: black;\n      font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n    }\n<\/style>\n<p><strong>In all of our interactions, we are guided by these values<\/strong><\/p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-pullquote\"><blockquote><p>KNOWLEDGE<\/p><cite>To encourage the process of learning<br>To celebrate truth-seeking through discourse and investigation<br>To anticipate and contribute to scholarly inquiry<br>To promote the library as both real and virtual extended classroom<br>To embrace the role as collectors and custodians of intellectual records<\/cite><\/blockquote><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-pullquote\"><blockquote><p>SERVICE<\/p><cite>To offer an environment that supports creativity, flexibility, and collaboration<br>To emphasize that each user of the Library is unique and important<br>To resolve to meet the changing needs of the library and its users<br>To maintain a comfortable, welcoming, and safe place of study, research, and interaction<\/cite><\/blockquote><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-pullquote\"><blockquote><p>QUALITY<\/p><cite>To achieve excellence<br>To seek out the best people and resources for work<br>To support individual growth and faculty development<br>To work diligently to exceed the expectations of services rendered<\/cite><\/blockquote><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-pullquote\"><blockquote><p>INTEGRITY<\/p><cite>To relate to each other with honesty and candour<br>To adhere to the principles of fairness, justice, and equality in the workplace<br>To promote the highest standards of professionalism, including open and equitable access to information.<br>To demonstrate a strong work ethic, taken responsibility for actions and commitments<\/cite><\/blockquote><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-pullquote\"><blockquote><p>RESPECT<\/p><cite>To treat all staff and student with equal consideration and courtesy<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To encourage differences in perspective, opinions, and ideas<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To provide an environment that is inclusive and diverse<\/cite><\/blockquote><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-pullquote\"><blockquote><p>COMMUNICATION<\/p><cite>To engage in open and honest communication at all levels<br>To recognize the importance of Library-wide participation<br>To reach out to all segment of the user community<br>To share information and solicit opinions about decisions that affect the success of the Library<\/cite><\/blockquote><\/figure>\n\n\n<p><\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In all of our interactions, we are guided by these values KNOWLEDGE To encourage the process of learningTo celebrate truth-seeking through discourse and investigationTo anticipate and contribute to scholarly inquiryTo promote the library as both real and virtual extended classroomTo embrace the role as collectors and custodians of intellectual records SERVICE To offer an environment [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":271,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"full-width.php","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/library.ttu.edu.gh\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/101"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/library.ttu.edu.gh\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/library.ttu.edu.gh\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/library.ttu.edu.gh\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"